room_title: Escape room "The Lighthouse" by Escape Ithaca in Ithaca
room_description: Sailing a bad storm, a familiar beacon of hope cuts through the rain – a lighthouse! You direct your men to seek refuge there to weather the storm. Greeted by the keeper, Captain White, a jolly old man, you withdraw to your quarters. But wait. Lighthouses don’t have keepers. As you rush to tell your men, you realize all the doors are locked and windows are barred. What will you do next?
